# Albion Greens — Environment Variables
# Copy to .env.local for local dev. Add to Vercel → Settings → Environment Variables for production.

RESEND_API_KEY=re_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Sign up free at https://resend.com (3,000 emails/month free)
# Create an API key in Dashboard → API Keys, paste it above.
#
# Domain setup (recommended): In Resend → Domains, add albiongreens.co.uk
# and follow the DNS instructions. Until then, swap the "from" addresses
# in pages/api/*.js to onboarding@resend.dev for testing.
